              60 minutes or less – fast and reliable.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Tyre Fitting</strong>: Our expert technicians will replace
              your flat tyre quickly and safely.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Payment</strong>: Choose your preferred payment method –
              cash or card – and you’re good to go!
            </li>
          </ol>
        </div>
